NAME
    Alien::libwebsockets - Find or build libwebsockets C library

SYNOPSIS
    use Alien::libwebsockets;
    my $cflags = Alien::libwebsockets->cflags;
    my $libs = Alien::libwebsockets->libs;

DESCRIPTION
    This Alien module provides libwebsockets for use by other Perl modules.
    When built from source, it is configured with libev, SSL, zlib, and
    permessage-deflate extension support.

